      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. NOSEY BLUEY produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 515m behind Flying Ducati (29.97) in a Grade 5 FIN. Has ability and looks hard to stop. 6. DR. WARREN was in the minors two back (30.01) at this track but ran below best last time at Sale, finishing 6th. Cannot be underestimated. 8. DURAN OLLY had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (34.78) at this track in a Grade 5 over 595m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Sure to be thereabouts. 1. DR. EXCLAIM is worth including after a top-three finish in slick time most recently.\",\"runners\":[5,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
